data.description: Have you dreamed of owning your own mini farm? Now is your chance! This brick home has so much to offer. 3 beds 2 bathrooms, walk-in shower, kitchen appliances. There is an additional room that could be used as a 4th bedroom, storage, or office space. Roof is less than 2 years old. The outside features a large 40x40 barn with 4 horse stalls, tack room, and half bathroom. In addition, there is an extra 18x24 workshop for additional storage. Various fruit and mature trees provide a beautiful setting. Some of the property is already fenced and ready for animals. Country living yet close to amenities. Approx. 20 minutes to Florence AL.
